reviewText: My four kids sing the songs and have fond memories of the songs and video. Thank you to Karyn for passing fundamental truths about God's love and grace and our need of a Savior.
My children love Karen Henley!! My older children grew up with her and when I had two more children (10 yrs later) I couldn't imagine them growing up without her.  My 2 yr old LOVES GROW GROW GROW.
Still just as entertaining as when it first came out. Grands love it just like their parents did.

This dvd will keep your little one's attention at a much younger age than 2. I have bought several of these dvd's for my children, grandchildren and now my 19 month great grandaughter loves it. It teaches them a lot about God's love plus about colors, animals, counting, etc.
Cute songs, I just love the other DVDs of hers better.
Karyn Henley DVD's are the BEST.
My preschooler loves this!  Catchy tunes that adults will enjoy too.  Pearls of truth in every song teaching children about God.  Super.  A+
This is an excellent video for babies. I bought this for my new granchild because my other grandchild had enjoyed it so much when he was little.

As I wrote in my other reviews, I believe Henley touches preschoolers to their inner being. Great message and very "safe" viewing for littles with no worries with the added plus of God's message. This DVD is a replacement for VHS tape in our church library - all set for new eyes!
